    "class": "gps-607398429357769626 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_ARTICLE&editorId=607381796862034487&sectionId=607398429357769626)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggw9OQm_-4__text","label":"ggw9OQm_-4__text","default":"So Having Higher Amounts Of Progeline In<br>Your Skin Means You Have The Skin Structure<br>Of Someone Decades Younger (Whether You Actually Are That Age Or Not!)"},{"type":"html","id":"ggh534PZbLV_text","label":"ggh534PZbLV_text","default":"<p>Loss of firmness, wrinkles, thin crepey skin, jowls, turkey neck, and sagging... if it sounds incredible that all of these aging concerns are associated with just one protein, believe me, it is!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_fFEmlmop_text","label":"gg_fFEmlmop_text","default":"<p>But it's not surprising when you remember what's happening in most women's skin... We've been aging faster than ever before. Every day we're exposed to UV rays, pollution, stress, and skincare products that actually accelerate aging rather than prevent it.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvGcfqaX3X_text","label":"ggvGcfqaX3X_text","default":"<p>Not to mention our modern lifestyle that increases Progerin, the “bad”production dramatically, letting it build up in our skin cells and causing us to age before our time.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkcaQKNIQg_text","label":"ggkcaQKNIQg_text","default":"<p>When your skin has high levels of Progerin, these factors create havoc on our appearance, making us look years or even decades older than we should.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEkbdvfi5c_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggEkbdvfi5c_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9img1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHl01M2giV_text","label":"ggHl01M2giV_text","default":"<p>Research from the <strong>Society of Cosmetic Chemists</strong> revealed something startling...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEi-UC_QMq_text","label":"ggEi-UC_QMq_text","default":"<p>When they studied how women age, they discovered Progerin increases by 3% every year. By the time a woman reaches 40, her levels become so high it begins to show dramatically in her appearance.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcAP1zJucy_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggcAP1zJucy_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9img1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJwUlql5FY_text","label":"ggJwUlql5FY_text","default":"<p><strong>This Explains Why So Many Women Find:</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAy1HlRgtH_childItem_0","label":"ggAy1HlRgtH_childItem_0","default":"<p>Their skin suddenly looking thin and crepey</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAy1HlRgtH_childItem_1","label":"ggAy1HlRgtH_childItem_1","default":"<p>Loss of firmness happening rapidly</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAy1HlRgtH_childItem_2","label":"ggAy1HlRgtH_childItem_2","default":"<p>Deep wrinkles forming seemingly overnight</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAy1HlRgtH_childItem_3","label":"ggAy1HlRgtH_childItem_3","default":"<p>Sagging along the jawline and neck</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAy1HlRgtH_childItem_4","label":"ggAy1HlRgtH_childItem_4","default":"<p>A tired, aged appearance no matter what creams they try</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfsfO2owSZ_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggfsfO2owSZ_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9bx1bg.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNyq97XzV5_text","label":"ggNyq97XzV5_text","default":"<p>According to my research and that of other leading dermatologists, high Progerin levels are now considered the root cause of aging skin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWXj68qFWk_text","label":"ggWXj68qFWk_text","default":"<p>Looking At Skin Samples From My Patients, I Discovered Something That Nobody Else Had Noticed:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gguejlQZWv8_childItem_0","label":"gguejlQZWv8_childItem_0","default":"<p>When Progerin builds up, it destroys collagen</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gguejlQZWv8_childItem_1","label":"gguejlQZWv8_childItem_1","default":"<p>It makes our skin thinner</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gguejlQZWv8_childItem_2","label":"gguejlQZWv8_childItem_2","default":"<p>It eats away at elastin</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gguejlQZWv8_childItem_3","label":"gguejlQZWv8_childItem_3","default":"<p>It reduces firmness</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gguejlQZWv8_childItem_4","label":"gguejlQZWv8_childItem_4","default":"<p>It creates that loose, saggy appearance we all dread</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtQfhBasUV_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggtQfhBasUV_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9bx2img.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggf46UiPuCN_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggf46UiPuCN_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9img2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtuQzix9i8_text","label":"ggtuQzix9i8_text","default":"<p>But here's what's most concerning...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-Ywhr1fFd_text","label":"gg-Ywhr1fFd_text","default":"<p>The Advances in Dermatology Study in 2012 showed something even more alarming: exposure to <strong>UVA rays from the sun significantly increases the amount of Progerin in our skin.</strong> Which is why excessive tanning prematurely ages us.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0LZtBCh-d_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg0LZtBCh-d_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9img2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDghRP7tzj_text","label":"ggDghRP7tzj_text","default":"<p>And modern life makes this even worse. We're exposed to more environmental toxins, stress, and artificial ingredients than ever before -- all of which can accelerate Progerin production.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-7rFI8NP8_text","label":"gg-7rFI8NP8_text","default":"<p>The \"anti-aging\" industry knows this is happening. But instead of addressing the root cause, they keep selling temporary fixes that just mask the problem.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggN70CImHmA_text","label":"ggN70CImHmA_text","default":"<p>Even worse, many expensive creams and treatments contain ingredients that can actually increase Progerin levels - making your skin age faster while promising to make you look younger!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvAls4Yr0I_text","label":"ggvAls4Yr0I_text","default":"<p>That's why I refused to recommend any traditional anti-aging products to my patients.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbZCw8FFgD_text","label":"ggbZCw8FFgD_text","default":"<p>You See, Most \"Solutions\" Focus On:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBDqb5qhkA_childItem_0","label":"ggBDqb5qhkA_childItem_0","default":"<p>Adding more collagen (which can't penetrate deeply enough)</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBDqb5qhkA_childItem_1","label":"ggBDqb5qhkA_childItem_1","default":"<p>Temporary plumping with hyaluronic acid</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBDqb5qhkA_childItem_2","label":"ggBDqb5qhkA_childItem_2","default":"<p>Quick-fix tightening agents</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBDqb5qhkA_childItem_3","label":"ggBDqb5qhkA_childItem_3","default":"<p>Protecting from sun damage</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBDqb5qhkA_childItem_4","label":"ggBDqb5qhkA_childItem_4","default":"<p>Masking imperfections with silicones</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggoxbr_0le0_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggoxbr_0le0_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9bx3bg.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKnW-9rKsc_text","label":"ggKnW-9rKsc_text","default":"<p><strong>But none of these address the real problem – rising Progerin levels that are aging us prematurely.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggExhhDWLWe_text","label":"ggExhhDWLWe_text","default":"<p>When I looked closely at the research and compared it to what I was seeing in my own patients, I began to notice something that nobody else had seen...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOndC3cyGS_text","label":"ggOndC3cyGS_text","default":"<p>The women who maintained youthful skin the longest all had something in common. Their skin cells showed remarkably lower levels of Progerin, similar to women decades younger.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEnDX3ooFb_text","label":"ggEnDX3ooFb_text","default":"<p>This wasn't just a coincidence. Their skin was actually functioning like that of a much younger person.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUAj1-W08S_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggUAj1-W08S_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9img3.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggx58kR-9bv_text","label":"ggx58kR-9bv_text","default":"<p><strong>Plus, studying these women's skin revealed something else extraordinary...</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gguCn0NkRPG_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gguCn0NkRPG_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9img3.png"}],
